    "en": {
      "title": "Couple arrested after killing and running away",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A young man and a young woman who tried to flee the country after committing a murder in Kalgisai were arrested at Katunayake Airport last night (30).",
        "A 31-year-old man and a 19-year-old woman were arrested while trying to flee to Dubai.",
        "Investigation revealed that the said duo had killed a person in Kalgissa area on 27th of this month, and the Katunayake Airport police were informed about it, and both were arrested at the airport."
      ],
